{"cid":"1576208565560333","cha_name":"肖战","desc":"肖战，1991年10月5日出生于重庆市，中国内地男演员、歌手。\n2015年，以选手的身份参加浙江卫视才艺养成选秀节目《燃烧吧少年》。2016年4月，主演校园星座超能力网络剧《超星星学园》。2018年4月25日，古装奇幻网络剧《哦！我的皇帝陛下》在腾讯视频播出，肖战凭北堂墨染一角崭露头角。2019年6月27日，领衔主演的古装仙侠剧《陈情令》在腾讯视频播出，肖战凭魏无羡一角赢得广泛关注。7月，主演的古装玄幻剧《斗罗大陆》正式杀青。8月，主演都市情感剧《余生，请多指教》。9月13日，主演的古装仙侠电影《诛仙I》在全国上映。2020年1月24日，肖战首次登上中央广播电视总台春节联欢晚会，与谢娜等合作表演小品《喜欢你，喜欢我》。2月2日，参与演唱的抗疫主题歌曲《坚信爱会赢》及MV正式首发。4月25日零点，歌曲《光点》正式上线。11月19日，参演的古装言情传奇剧《狼殿下》播出，肖战在剧中饰演落拓不羁的赏金猎人疾冲。\n现有待播剧：《余生，请多指教》、《斗罗大陆》。","schema":"aweme://aweme/challenge/detail?cid=1576208565560333","author":{"uid":"6796248446","short_id":"52","nickname":"抖音小助手","gender":1,"signature":"本宝宝暂时还没想到个性签名","avatar_larger":{"uri":"1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p3.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p9.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p29.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_thumb":{"uri":"100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p6.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p29.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p3.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_medium":{"uri":"720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p9.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p6.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p29.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"birthday":"","is_verified":true,"follow_status":0,"aweme_count":0,"following_count":0,"follower_count":0,"favoriting_count":0,"total_favorited":0,"is_block":false,"hide_search":true,"constellation":10,"location":"","hide_location":false,"weibo_verify":"","custom_verify":"","unique_id":"douyin","bind_phone":" {"cid":"1572072504832002","cha_name":"王一博","desc":"王一博，中国内地男歌手、演员、职业摩托车赛车手，1997年8月5日出生于河南洛阳。2014年9月15日，作为UNIQ组合成员出道，2016年4月加入《天天向上》。第30届中国电视金鹰奖观众喜爱的男演员。《陪你到世界之巅》饰季向空，《陈情令》饰蓝忘机，《有翡》饰谢允，《冰雨火》饰陈宇，《风起洛阳》饰百里弘毅。","schema":"aweme://aweme/challenge/detail?cid=1572072504832002","author":{"uid":"101562100101","short_id":"2014940272","nickname":"王一博吧_WYBBar","gender":1,"signature":"王一博是最酷的盖","avatar_larger":{"uri":"1080x1080/tos-cn-i-0813/8df124c4611a4037b6d6e207f56391ce","url_list":["https://p3.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/8df124c4611a4037b6d6e207f56391ce~c5_1080x1080.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p29.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/8df124c4611a4037b6d6e207f56391ce~c5_1080x1080.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p26.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/8df124c4611a4037b6d6e207f56391ce~c5_1080x1080.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_thumb":{"uri":"100x100/tos-cn-i-0813/8df124c4611a4037b6d6e207f56391ce","url_list":["https://p9.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/8df124c4611a4037b6d6e207f56391ce~c5_100x100.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p29.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/8df124c4611a4037b6d6e207f56391ce~c5_100x100.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p26.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/8df124c4611a4037b6d6e207f56391ce~c5_100x100.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_medium":{"uri":"720x720/tos-cn-i-0813/8df124c4611a4037b6d6e207f56391ce","url_list":["https://p3.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/8df124c4611a4037b6d6e207f56391ce~c5_720x720.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p26.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/8df124c4611a4037b6d6e207f56391ce~c5_720x720.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p29.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/8df124c4611a4037b6d6e207f56391ce~c5_720x720.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"birthday":"","is_verified":true,"follow_status":0,"aweme_count":0,"following_count":0,"follower_count":0,"favoriting_count":0,"total_favorited":0,"is_block":false,"hide_search":true,"constellation":10,"location":"","hide_location":false,"weibo_verify":"","custom_v
